ET ELECTRONICS, JAEO CHEMICAL, OK PHARMA

150
00:11:30,523 --> 00:11:32,233
ET ELECTRONICS, JAEO CHEMICAL, OK PHARMA

151
00:11:33,984 --> 00:11:35,236
(exhales heavily)

152
