(sirens wailing)

189
00:14:21,193 --> 00:14:23,195
(music stops)

190
00:14:26,156 --> 00:14:28,158
-What is it?
-What?

191
00:14:29,702 --> 00:14:33,414
Just say it. Stop glancing at me
and making me uncomfortable.

192
00:14:38,085 --> 00:14:39,420
It's not you, is it?

193
00:14:39,503 --> 00:14:40,921
Didn't you say...

194
00:14:41,881 --> 00:14:44,133
