00:35:17,782 --> 00:35:19,075
INMATES: Big! Big!

567
00:35:20,827 --> 00:35:22,328
(breathes deeply)

568
00:35:23,371 --> 00:35:24,914
Say something, will you?

569
00:35:24,997 --> 00:35:27,083
DOOGEUN:
A solution won't fall on our laps!

570
00:35:27,917 --> 00:35:29,252
CHAEBONG: A solution to what?

571
00:35:29,335 --> 00:35:33,089
