751
00:50:23,687 --> 00:50:25,147
Hello, ma'am.

752
00:50:26,273 --> 00:50:29,276
We were out of surgical masks
and alcohol pads.

753
00:50:30,944 --> 00:50:34,573
You came all the way here for that
instead of the supply room in the ward?

754
00:50:34,656 --> 00:50:35,866
(chuckles)

755
00:50:37,242 --> 00:50:39,119
What brings you here?

756
00:50:40,912 --> 00:50:44,166
I stopped by the center
and saw you come in here.

757
00:50:45,333 --> 00:50:47,794
Then you must've seen
the head nurse come in as well.

758
00:50:47,878 --> 00:50:49,880
(suspenseful music)

759
00:50:52,549 --> 00:50:53,592
(door closes)

760
00:51:00,015 --> 00:51:01,933
MIHO: She came in and disappeared.

761
00:51:02,726 --> 00:51:06,438
I know I saw her come in here.
I don't know what happened.

762
00:51:06,521 --> 00:51:07,981
MIHO: If you know...

763
00:51:08,065 --> 00:51:10,984
I was watching the security videos...

764
00:51:11,568 --> 00:51:12,778
You saw the head nurse, right?

765
00:51:12,861 --> 00:51:14,196
She was the only person...

766
00:51:15,447 --> 00:51:16,823
that I saw.

767
00:51:17,657 --> 00:51:18,658
(scoffs)

768
00:51:20,619 --> 00:51:23,622
Wait. Are you saying I followed a ghost?

769
00:51:23,705 --> 00:51:26,041
There is one reason why I pay you.

770
00:51:26,541 --> 00:51:27,709
It's simple.

771
00:51:29,002 --> 00:51:30,545
To look after patients.

772
00:51:32,130 --> 00:51:34,341
If you do something unnecessary again,

773
00:51:35,133 --> 00:51:38,512
I'll take that nurse's uniform
off of you myself.

774
00:51:38,595 --> 00:51:40,597
(suspenseful music)

775
00:51:54,194 --> 00:51:55,237
(sighs)

776
00:52:04,496 --> 00:52:06,498
(ominous music)

777
00:52:06,873 --> 00:52:10,585
How long have you worked here, Mr. Ham?

778
00:52:11,294 --> 00:52:12,754
This is my 31st year.

779
00:52:13,255 --> 00:52:16,258
I've worked in the supply room
for 24 years.

780
00:52:18,260 --> 00:52:19,970
Don't go inside.

781
00:52:21,513 --> 00:52:24,432
MR. HAM: That's the same thing
the previous director said.

782
00:52:30,564 --> 00:52:32,566
(music intensifies)

783
00:52:37,612 --> 00:52:41,199
DOOGEUN: You don't know how it is here.
Every day is a living hell.

784
00:52:41,283 --> 00:52:43,201
We're dying more and more every day.

785
00:52:43,285 --> 00:52:44,703
So what?

786
00:52:45,287 --> 00:52:49,499
You'll confess to everything at trial
because you're afraid of that punk?

787
00:52:49,583 --> 00:52:53,712
